Cardboard sleeve (mini LP) reissue from Elvin Bishop features the high-fidelity SHM-CD format (compatible with standard CD players). The cardboard sleeve faithfully replicates its first pressing US LP artwork, including company sleeve. Comes with an obi that replicates the first pressing Japanese edition, lyrics, and a description. Part of a 6-album Elvin Bishop mini LP SHM-CD reissue series featuring albums "Let It Flow," "Juke Joint Jump," "Struttin' My Stuff," "Hometown Boy Makes Good!," "Raisin' Hell," and "Hog Heaven
